{"tid":28529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸ATM插卡槽現疑似讀卡器　港有同類設計","createTime":"2016-12-08T03:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T08:14:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de0b0dda7a877a01a7b276aa6ae734cd39fa423b","tid":28529,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161207/bkncn-20161207141537448-1207_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161207%2Fbkncn-20161207141537448-1207_05011_001.html&d=T%2FS5IpksPVt9v4yNcky7FoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=9c735db1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161207/bkncn-20161207141537448-1207_05011_001.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161207/photo/bkncn-20161207141537448-1207_05011_001_02b.jpg?20161207163034\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161207%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161207141537448-1207_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20161207163034&h=98c1e707&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161207/photo/bkncn-20161207141537448-1207_05011_001_03b.jpg?20161207163034\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161207%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161207141537448-1207_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20161207163034&h=19e48220&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n使用自動櫃員機（ATM）時必須細心留意機上有否被安裝額外裝置！內地網絡近日瘋傳一段短片，一部ATM的插卡槽上竟被人裝上一個與插卡槽一模一樣的神秘裝置，估計是詐騙集團用作套取受害人銀行卡或信用卡資料之用。 <br />\n<br />\n讀者徐先生向東網記者表示，近日內地瘋傳一段短片，在一部不明地點的ATM的插卡槽之上，有人安裝了一個一模一樣的裝置，拆下後更可見到背後有不少電子零件，懷疑是讀卡器。 <br />\n<br />\n從影片中的對話推斷，警方正調查涉事ATM，並表示附近已安裝閉路電視，只要待疑犯前來取走裝置，就能將其當場擒獲。警方又認為，施行這種手法的人，背後應有龐大集團支援。 <br />\n<br />\n徐先生坦言，香港不少ATM插卡槽的設計，都與短片中的十分類似，擔心詐騙集團會將此種手法「引入」香港，令不知情的港人蒙受損失。"},{"pid":"ebcf4dfc49f79c3e12f3b6f6755d534c3902468b","tid":28529,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e352ae1e5e30a3869c9c32f9bc449b2e1a5b6d9","tid":28529,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"防不勝防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a8f5e8dfa92b271f42ec5a8d2ac6dff463f5bd","tid":28529,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"支那仲未用晶片？"},{"pid":"5f460e1e42382505e653a23014109a46c3c33136","tid":28529,"uid":8198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:39:40.000Z","msg":"遲早要學班廢老去櫃檯攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516932ad44bef3b764721fec04ee410096ad569a","tid":28529,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那仲未用晶片？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晶片可以防到？<br />\n<br />\n早排有部中銀機比人裝左讀卡器，照計香港中銀卡都變哂晶片啦"},{"pid":"e0dabdbeea7bd37e2c26d0ee7509d3b5a67ce60b","tid":28529,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那仲未用晶片？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n晶片可以防到？<br />\n<br />\n早排有部中銀機比人裝左讀卡器，照計香港中銀卡都變哂晶片啦</blockquote><br />\n圖入面個個野係讀磁帶"},{"pid":"8a1c0e1d17b22b6fc040b5d2e5e1b83dbda1a66b","tid":28529,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"Youtube有鬼佬拍過片"},{"pid":"09c98e59cf216f3faab5e90a7f232e3d7dc24a9d","tid":28529,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}